<p>This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which MindBricks Pvt Ltd collects, uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users (each, a "User") of the facetimes.com website ("Site"). This privacy policy applies to the Site and all products and services offered by MindBricks Pvt Ltd.</p>

